text: Diego Alejandro Cuadros Velásquez (born 28 May 1996) is a Colombian footballer who currently plays as a midfielder for Alianza Petrolera. ==Club career== ===FK Senica=== Diego Cuadros made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for SenicaFC Spartak a.s., Trnava - FK Senica 1:0 24.02.2018, futbalnet.sk against Spartak Trnava on February 24, 2018. After his loan spell at Senica, Cuadros joined the club permanently. But he was released at the end of 2018.Senica hlási prvú zimnú posilu, rozširuje aj realizačný tím, profutbal.sk, 18 December 2018 ===AEZ Zakakiou=== On 31 January 2019, the Cyprus Football Association confirmed, that Cuadros had joined AEZ Zakakiou in the Cypriot Second Division.Ενημέρωση για τις μεταγραφές (31/01/2019), cfa.com.cy, 31 January 2019Κίνηση με Diego Cuadros!, kerkida.net, 31 January 2019 ===Alianza Petrolera=== In the summer 2019, Cuadros returned to Colombia and signed with Alianza Petrolera.Alianza Petrolera se refuerza con dos colombianos procedentes del exterior, golombianos.com, 7 July 2019 ==References== ==External links== * Futbalnet profile * * Diego Cuadros at CFA Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:People from Antioquia Department Category:Colombian footballers Category:Colombian expatriate footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:Caracas FC players Category:Jaguares de Córdoba footballers Category:FK Senica players Category:AEZ Zakakiou players Category:Alianza Petrolera players Category:Categoría Primera A players Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Cypriot Second Division players Category:Expatriate footballers in Slovakia Category:Expatriate footballers in Cyprus Category:Colombian expatriate sportspeople in Slovakia Category:Colombian expatriate sportspeople in Cyprus
